title: InqScribe 2.0.5 and ExpressScribe 5.5
description:
Two great soft wares for people into transcription. 

InqScribe and Express Scribe

If you are looking for these then you know what are are. Both are up and working on my PC. Hard to track down the serial fro InqScribe but I found a working one after an hour or so of rummaging through nasty serial sites. Express Scribe has a working KG.

As far as I can tell both are up and running. PC only here.

Uranium Willy
